00:08:53.049 --> 00:08:59.850
throughout the entire country, a total of 115,453 attended.

00:08:59.950 --> 00:09:03.850
And a highlight of Ecuador's theoretical history was the international convention

00:09:03.850 --> 00:09:07.450
that was held there in January this year.

00:09:07.450 --> 00:09:11.450
And it was just an evidence of Jehovah's continued blessing of the work there

00:09:11.450 --> 00:09:16.649
since the preaching work started there back in 1935.

