00:09:24.950 --> 00:09:30.350
And he alluded to the growth in his dedication talk back there in 1994.

00:09:30.350 --> 00:09:34.649
At that time, when he was there, there were 26,000 publishers in Ecuador.

00:09:34.649 --> 00:09:39.149
